sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant HTTP as caikit Runtime<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    participant GRPC as caikit Runtime<br/>gRPC 8085/TCP
    participant TextGen as TextGeneration<br/>(Local Module)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(TGIS Module)
    participant PeftTrain as PeftPromptTuning<br/>(Training)
    participant PeftTGIS as PeftPromptTuningTGIS<br/>(TGIS Module)
    participant EmbMod as EmbeddingModule<br/>(Embeddings)
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(GPU/CPU Memory)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Server<br/>gRPC (configurable port)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformer<br/>(In-Memory)
    participant Disk as Local Disk<br/>(Prompt Vectors)

    Note over Client,STModel: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>TextGen: Python call (in-process)
    TextGen->>HFModel: PyTorch inference
    HFModel-->>TextGen: Generated text
    TextGen-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: TGIS Remote Text Generation

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>TextGenTGIS: Python call (in-process)
    TextGenTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationService<br/>TLS optional / mTLS optional
    TGIS-->>TextGenTGIS: Generated text
    TextGenTGIS-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,STModel: Flow 3: Text Embedding

    Client->>GRPC: gRPC NlpService.EmbeddingTaskPredict<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    GRPC->>EmbMod: Python call (in-process)
    EmbMod->>STModel: SentenceTransformer.encode()
    STModel-->>EmbMod: Embedding vectors
    EmbMod-->>GRPC: Response
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC Response

    Note over Client,Disk: Flow 4: Prompt Tuning Training

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/train<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>PeftTrain: Python call (in-process)
    PeftTrain->>HFModel: Load frozen base model
    HFModel-->>PeftTrain: Model loaded
    PeftTrain->>PeftTrain: PEFT training loop<br/>(Accelerate mixed-precision)
    PeftTrain->>Disk: Save prompt vectors<br/>(encoder.pt / decoder.pt)
    PeftTrain-->>HTTP: Training complete
    HTTP-->>Client: Training result

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 5: TGIS Prompt Tuning Inference

    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>Auth: Delegated to platform
    HTTP->>PeftTGIS: Python call (in-process)
    PeftTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC with prompt cache ID<br/>TLS optional / mTLS optional
    TGIS-->>PeftTGIS: Generated text
    PeftTGIS-->>HTTP: Response
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response
